        protected OnFlyCallGraphBuilder createOnFlyCallGraphBuilder​(ContextManager cm,
                                                            ReachableMethods reachableMethods,
                                                            boolean appOnly)
        Factory method for creating a new on-fly callgraph builder. Custom implementations can override this method for injecting own callgraph builders without having to modify Soot.
        Parameters:
        cm - The context manager
        reachableMethods - The reachable method set
        appOnly - True to only consider application code
        Returns:
        The new on-fly callgraph builder
